Package: deepToolsUtils
Type: Package
Title: Pre and postprocessing functions for HTS data analysis using deepTools.
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Sebastian Kurscheid [aut, cre]
Maintainer: Sebastian Kurscheid <sebastian.kurscheid@anu.edu.au>
Depends: R (>= 3.3.0), GenomicFeatures, curl, biomaRt
Suggests: GenomicRanges
Description: This is a collection of stand-alone functions which can be deployed in a snakemake workflow in order to create e.g. region files in BED format from existing annotation such as Ensembl GTF files. These BED files can then be used in the deepTool analysis steps for e.g. creating metagene plots over selected genomic features. Further functions will be added for the post-processing of deepTools output, such as the integration of gene expression data or other epigenomic data sets.
License: MIT
URL: https://github.com/skurscheid/deepToolsUtils
BugReports: https://github.com/skurscheid/deepToolsUtils/issues
LazyData: TRUE
